snippet.title: Project Hedra - Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1009960/Project_Hedra/

Experience endless adventures with Project Hedra, the open-world low-poly exploration game that puts procedurally generated content at the forefront of gameplay. Inspired by games like CubeWorld, Minecraft, and Diablo II, Project Hedra offers infinite replayability and a unique world to explore every time you play.
